==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Passiflora
<hw>Pas"si*flo"ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL., from
L. <ets>passio</ets> passion (fr. <ets>pati</ets>, <ets>passus</ets>, to
suffer) + <ets>flos</ets>, <ets>floris</ets>, flower.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of plants, including the passion flower.
It is the type of the order <ord>Passiflore⟦ae⟧</ord>, which includes
about nineteen genera and two hundred and fifty species.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Passifloraceae</ent>⟦br⟧
